item.description:
Come join us for an open Midsummer Celebration! :)

Scheduled events will include: Ritual with High Priestess Tala and Chanting in circle by Kellianna :)

Battle of the Oak & Holly King, Spiral Dance, Pot Luck Dinner, and Bonfire, Wicker man & Drumming & Chanting around the fire with Kellianna! :)

Pot luck sign up sheet will be sent out a couple of weeks prior to the celebration.

Alcoholic Drinking is BYOB

Donations will be accepted to cover the paper products and porta potty costs

Overnight camping is available, please specify.

Arrival time is 2:00 pm Ritual will be starting at 3:00 pm.
item.why: You will have alot of fun! :)
item.name: Open Midsummer Celebration
